== 退休球衣號碼 ==
灰熊宣布計劃在2022年1月28日退役[[托尼·阿伦|托尼·阿伦]]的9號<ref name="AllenRandolph">{{cite web |title=Memphis Grizzlies to retire Zach Randolph and Tony Allen jerseys |url=https://www.nba.com/news/memphis-grizzlies-to-retire-zach-randolph-and-tony-allen-jerseys |website=NBA.com |access-date=September 6, 2021 |date=September 1, 2021 |archive-date=2022-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220511103913/https://www.nba.com/news/memphis-grizzlies-to-retire-zach-randolph-and-tony-allen-jerseys }}</ref>。在2018-19賽季的交易截止日交易了[[馬克·蓋索|馬克·蓋索]]之後，球隊宣佈蓋索的33號將退役<ref>{{cite web |title=Memphis Grizzlies release statement on Marc Gasol from controlling owner Robert Pera |url=https://www.nba.com/grizzlies/news/memphis-grizzlies-release-statement-on-marc-gasol-190208 |website=NBA.com |access-date=February 9, 2019 |date=February 8, 2019 |archive-date=2021-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211213050943/https://www.nba.com/grizzlies/news/memphis-grizzlies-release-statement-on-marc-gasol-190208 }}</ref>。在交易了[[邁克·康利|邁克·康利]]之後，球隊宣布他們將退役康利的11號球衣<ref>{{cite web |title=Memphis Grizzlies release statement on Mike Conley from owner Robert J. Pera |url=https://www.nba.com/grizzlies/news/memphis-grizzlies-release-statement-on-mike-conley-from-owner-robert-j-pera-190706 |website=NBA.com |access-date=May 2, 2021 |date=July 6, 2019 |archive-date=2022-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220515073454/https://www.nba.com/grizzlies/news/memphis-grizzlies-release-statement-on-mike-conley-from-owner-robert-j-pera-190706 }}</ref>。 2021年11月24日，在聯邦對東尼·阿倫的前NBA球員詐保案件進行調查期間，阿倫要求灰熊延期他的球衣退役<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tony Allen asks Grizzlies to postpone jersey retirement|url=https://www.msn.com/en-us/sports/nba/tony-allen-asks-grizzlies-to-postpone-jersey-retirement/ar-AARbhD8?li=BB15ms5q|access-date=2021-12-09|website=www.msn.com|archive-date=2021-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211209204903/https://www.msn.com/en-us/sports/nba/tony-allen-asks-grizzlies-to-postpone-jersey-retirement/ar-AARbhD8?li=BB15ms5q}}</ref>。
